Gods from Tortall quiz
[INS::INS]
Fun Trivia

These question all have to do with the Gods mentioned in both the "Song of the Lioness" quartet and "The Immortals" quartet.

Average score for this quiz is 8 / 10. Difficulty: Easy. Played 1,101 times. As of Nov 20 17.
1. Where does Alanna first meet the Great Mother Goddess?

( ) in the black city
( ) in a dream
( ) under a tree
( ) during the ordeal


NEXT>

2. The Master of all Death is also known by another name. What is this name?

( ) Black God
( ) Dark God
( ) Hades
( ) Mithros


NEXT>

3. What is the name of the Dream God?

( ) Star
( ) Daniel
( ) Gainel
( ) Gunapi


NEXT>

4. Which one of the following does NOT apply to Mithros?

( ) God of Mercy
( ) God of War and Law
( ) Chief of Gods
( ) Sun God


NEXT>

5. Which country is the Graveyard Hag the Patron God of?

( ) Scanra
( ) Santen
( ) Smiskir
( ) Carthak


NEXT>

6. Kidunka the Lord of the Banjiku tribes is also known as the "world" something. What is it?

( ) Dragon
( ) Snake
( ) Lizard
( ) Hyena


NEXT>

7. What are the parents of the Gods known as?

( ) Fire, Galaxy
( ) Flame, Universe
( ) Sun, Universe
( ) Flame, Galaxy


NEXT>

8. What is Uusoae the Queen of?

( ) Change
( ) Chaos
( ) War
( ) Humanity


NEXT>

9. Name the Three Sorrows.

( ) Slaughter, Disease, Starvation
( ) Death, Malady, Starvation
( ) Slaughter, Malady, Starvation
( ) Slaughter, Malady, Hunger


NEXT>

10. Sarra is Daine's mother, a midwife. She becomes a God, but what is her God name?

( ) White Lady
( ) Lady of Snowsdale
( ) Nature Lady
( ) Green Lady


